<P>THE Pri&s;oners being &s;et to the Bar, were arraigned on an Indictment for con&s;piring, combining and confe|derating with divers Negroes, to burn the whole Town and City of <HI>New-York;</HI> and to kill and de&s;troy the Inha|bitants thereof; and pleaded, <HI>Not Guilty:</HI> And for their Trials put them&s;elves upon God and the Country.</P>
