<P><HI>Sawney</HI> &s;aid, upon the Trial, <Q><HI>Jack</HI> was to be a Captain; that he a&s;ked him to help burn Hou&s;es; and &s;aid a&s;&s;oon as the Fort was burnt, they would kill the white Men: That <HI>Jack</HI> &s;wore &s;ix <HI>Spaniards,</HI> [Spani&s;h Slaves] and the re&s;t were to come next Day to be &s;worn.</Q></P>
