<P>This Day <HI>Ben</HI> (Capt. Mar&s;hall's) <HI>Qua&s;h</HI> (H. Rutgers's) <HI>Cae&s;ar</HI> (Kortrecht's) <HI>Toby</HI> alias <HI>Cato</HI> (Provoo&s;t's) <HI>Cato</HI> (Shurmur's) <HI>York</HI> and <HI>London</HI> (Mar&s;chalk's) <HI>Scipio</HI> (Van Bor&s;om's) and <HI>Harry</HI> (Furman's) were apprehended upon <HI>Jack</HI> (Comfort's) Examination and Confe&s;&s;ion, and com|mitted.</P>
<P>This Day al&s;o, The Negroes <HI>Cook, Robin</HI> (Chamber's) <HI>Cae&s;ar</HI> (Peck's) <HI>Cuffee</HI> (Gomez's) were executed according to Sentence.</P>
