<Q REND="margQuotes"><P>THAT <HI>Qua&s;h,</HI> Rutgers's, <HI>Quack,</HI> Roo&s;ewelt's, a&s;ked him one Sunday, if he would do as they would do? And <HI>Pompey</HI> a&s;ked them, What? And <HI>Qua&s;h</HI> &s;aid, <HI>Quack</HI> would tell him; and <HI>Quack</HI> &s;aid, they would &s;et their Ma&s;ter's Hou&s;es on fire, if he would &s;et his Ma&s;ter's Hou&s;e on fire; and he agreed he would; and they then told him, they would tell him when; and they would be all <HI>Free,</HI> and be free from Trouble: He a&s;ked what they de&s;igned to do? <HI>Quack</HI> &s;aid, they would tell him in Time, and would not tell him then.</P>
