<P>The Pri&s;oners a&s;ked the Witne&s;&s;es no material Que&s;tions, but upon their Defence denied all that was te&s;tified again&s;t them. Then</P>
<P>Mr. <HI>Murray</HI> &s;ummed up the Evidence again&s;t <HI>Ben, Qua&s;h,</HI> and <HI>Cato</HI> (COWLEY'S)</P>
<P>Mr. <HI>Chambers</HI> &s;ummed up the Evidence again&s;t <HI>Fortune,</HI> and <HI>Cato</HI> (PROVOOST'S)</P>
<P>Then the Jury being charged, withdrew for a little Time; and being returned, <HI>found</HI> them all <HI>Guilty</HI> of the Indictment.</P>
<P>Court adjourned till Monday Morning Ten o'Clock.</P>
<P>This Day <HI>Pedro</HI> (DE PEYSTER'S) <HI>Fortune</HI> and <HI>Tony</HI> (LATHAM'S) <HI>Prince</HI> (GABRIEL CROOKE'S) Negroes, were apprehended and committed.</P>
<Q><TEXT>
<BODY>
