<P N="1">1. He &s;aid, <Q REND="margQuotes">He was carried there by <HI>Albany</HI> la&s;t Whit&s;ontide was Twelve Months; and the &s;econd Time was about three Weeks after Chri&s;tma&s;s, when &s;everal Negroes pre&s;ent, <HI>Hugh&s;on, Wife, Daughter,</HI> and <HI>Peggy:</HI> When <HI>Hugh&s;on</HI> admini&s;tred the Oath on the Book, of <HI>Damnation to Eternity to them who failed or di&s;covered.</HI></Q></P>
