<P N="4">4. That <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> were &s;wo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters"> at <HI>Comfort'</HI>s, that is to &s;ay, Tho&s;e who were not &s;worn <HI>Hugh&s;on'</HI>s; The Oath was given by <HI>Ben,</HI> &s;omething of <HI>Thunder.</HI></P>
