<P><HI>He &s;aid,</HI></P>
<Q REND="margQuotes"><P>THAT in the Winter <HI>Hugh&s;on</HI> met him in the Woods, and carried him to his Hou&s;e, and gave him to drink, and a&s;ked him to join in the Con&s;piracy; and he con&s;ented, and <HI>was &s;worn by</HI> Hugh&s;on <HI>on a Book; that Thunder and Lightning might &s;trike him dead, if he did not comply,</HI> &amp;c.</P></Q>
<P><HI>He &s;aid,</HI> <Q REND="margQuotes">He was there in all, three Times; and named a few [Negroes] who were executed [that were there] but none el&s;e.</Q></P>
