<P><HI>WARWICK</HI> (Hunt's) <HI>&s;aid,</HI> <Q REND="margQuotes">That <HI>London,</HI> Wyn|coop's Negro, went with him to <HI>Hugh&s;on'</HI>s about two Years ago; that <HI>Hugh&s;on</HI> &s;wore him, in the Pre&s;ence of his <HI>Daughter, to kill his Ma&s;ter and Mi&s;tre&s;s;</HI> that <HI>he</HI> ordered the Pri&s;oner to &s;teal what Money he could and bring it to <HI>him, to buy Arms and Powder;</HI> that he, <HI>Hugh&s;on,</HI> had three Barrels of Powder, but wanted more: That he [<HI>Warwick</HI>] was <HI>there</HI> [at Hugh&s;on's] la&s;t chri&s;tma&s;s, at the GREAT SUPPER; but did not &s;ee all the Negroes that were there; he being in the Cellar, and in Liquor.</Q></P>
