<P><HI>LEWIS</HI> (Mr. Ad. Schuyler's) <HI>&s;aid,</HI> <Q REND="margQuotes">That on a Saturday Afternoon, Mr. Roo&s;evelt's <HI>Quack</HI> and Rut|gers's <HI>Qua&s;h,</HI> carried him to <HI>Hugh&s;on'</HI>s; that they drank Punch there; that he heard Nothing of the Plot at that Time; but <HI>Quack</HI> engaged him to come to him the next Day, which be did, at Mr. <HI>Rutgers'</HI>s Brew hou&s;e, where <HI>Quack &s;wore him,</HI> to <HI>fire his Ma&s;ter's Hou&s;e, and kill his Ma&s;ter and Mi&s;tre&s;s:</HI> That he afterwards &s;et fire to &s;ome Heading; but it being green, would not take fire. Knows of no others concerned.</Q></P>
