<P><HI>JACK</HI> (Abrahamse's) <HI>&s;aid,</HI> <Q REND="margQuotes">That a little before Chri&s;tma&s;s, <HI>Jack</HI> (Comfort's) and <HI>Cato</HI> (Cowley's) Carried him to <HI>Hugh&s;on'</HI>s, where they drank Punch; that then <HI>Hugh&s;on</HI> a&s;ked him&punc; whether he would be concerned with him <HI>to kill the white People?</HI> that he con&s;ented; and then <HI>Hugh&s;on</HI> told him he mu&s;t <HI>&s;wear,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> got a Book, and &s;wore <HI>the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> take him if he told any Body white or black;</HI> that wh<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;hould hear Fire cried <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> Night,</HI> he should kill his Ma&s;ter and Mi&s;tre&s;s, and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> to him, and he would <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> him a Gun and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">. That <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">here was a Woman <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;moaking, that &s;aw <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;worn, but don't know whether &s;he were <HI>Hugh&s;on<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> or who el&s;e.</Q></P>
