<Q REND="margQuotes"><P N="1">1. THAT the fir&s;t Time he was at <HI>Hugh&s;on's <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">e, Jack</HI> and <HI>Cook</HI> (Comfort's) drank a Pint of Rum together, and the Rum they bought at <HI>Hugh&s;on'</HI>s with the Money he had lo&s;t [at Play.]</P>
